<br>
EDIT: am lvl 56 <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uvadaarmonk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>VadaarMonk</A> at: 9/28/02 10:22:25 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/unorpin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Norpin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Grand High Poobah</span><br>  Posts: 4151<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/28/02 9:53:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11636.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Recently epic'd monk with a weapon question</span><hr size=1> It's hard to answer without knowing your level. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udindadar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dindadar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Young Grasshoppah</span><br>  Posts: 45<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/28/02 9:54:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11636.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Recently epic'd monk with a weapon question</span><hr size=1> Well, I gotta say Gold Inlaid Ulak is a NICE weapon, the lifetap proc will help imensly.  Put that in your primary i think...I'd say GIU + SoS combo.   <p>-Tyymm, 56th Enchanter<BR>
-Punches, 60th Monk<BR>
<a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=220640>Punches Majelo Profile</a><CENTER></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/unorpin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Norpin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Grand High Poobah</span><br>  Posts: 4153<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/28/02 10:18:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11636.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Recently epic'd monk with a weapon question</span><hr size=1> Putting a 28 delay weapon in primary at those levels is going to cut a huge chunk out of your damage.  You would need 2 unresisted procs a minute to get even close to the same damage the epic would in primary.<br>
<br>
It is a pretty safe bet IMHO that you will either want to be using the IFS, or the epic primary, GIU offhand combo (switching in the SoS for the proc). <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/unorpin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Norpin</A> at: 9/28/02 10:21:16 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ufraethir.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fraethir</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_bluespot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master</span><br>  Posts: 534<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/29/02 3:15:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11636.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Recently epic'd monk with a weapon question</span><hr size=1> I'd recommend epic/giu or ifs when you prefer 2hb. I gave up switching in and out a SoS because I usually use a tstaff (and truthfully, it bugged the hell out of me), AND I sometimes have whatever shaman buff overwrites/blocks the shielding series, so it was more or less a waste.<br>
<br>
Wish I had a GIU. That or the rhaag katar are about it for 1h upgrades 'within reach' for me.<br>
